## Notes & Considerations

### Authentication
- Current: Session-based authentication with cookies
- Supports password reset via email

### Database
- PostgreSQL for production
- SQLite for development/test (can be changed)

### API Structure
- RESTful design
- JSON responses
- Versioned endpoints (`/api/v1/`)

### CORS
- Configured in `config/initializers/cors.rb`
- Allow specific origins for security




